<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-EVSTQN3/azprG1Anm3QDgpJLIm9Nao0Yz1ztcQTwFspd3yD65VohhpuuCOmLASjC" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <title>Lernmaterial</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            color: #333;
        }
        header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        header img {
            width: 100%; /* Maximale Breite 100% */
            max-height: 100px; /* Maximale H√∂he auf 100px beschr√§nken */
            object-fit: cover; /* Das Bild wird gestreckt, um den verf√ºgbaren Platz zu f√ºllen */
        }
        section {
            width: 90%;
            margin: 20px auto;
        }
        .content-welcome {
            width: 70%;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        #back-to-top {
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 50px;
            right: 20px;
            display: none;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            background-color: rgba(0, 123, 255, 0.23);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 50%;
            font-size: 24px;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }
        #back-to-top:hover {
            background-color: rgba(0, 86, 179, 0.15);
            color: #fff;
            cursor: pointer;
        }
        footer {
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
            padding: 10px 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: fixed;
            bottom: 0;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <img src="rob-server/web/img/image.jpg" alt="Header Image">
</header>

<section id="tutorials">
    <div class="content-welcome">
        <h3>Entdecke Tutorials zu verschiedenen Themen</h3>
        <p>
            Unsere Lernplattform wurde geschaffen, um Ihre Bildungsreise zu unterst√ºtzen und Ihnen die Freiheit zu geben, in Ihrem eigenen Tempo zu lernen. Tauchen Sie ein in eine Welt des Wissens, in der flexible Lernzeiten.
        </p>
    </div>
</section>


<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

<a id="back-to-top" href="#" class="back-to-top">
    <i class="bi bi-arrow-up"></i>
    <span>ü°±</span>
</a>

<script>
    document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function () {
        var backToTopButton = document.getElementById('back-to-top');

        window.addEventListener('scroll', function () {
            if (window.pageYOffset > 100) {
                backToTopButton.style.display = 'block';
            } else {
                backToTopButton.style.display = 'none';
            }
        });

        backToTopButton.addEventListener('click', function (e) {
            e.preventDefault();
            window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: 'smooth' });
        });
    });
</script>

<footer>
    <div class="col-12">
        <div class="row d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center">
            &copy; 2024 Learn to Earn. Alle Rechte vorbehalten.
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>